OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773129873
OL,3,CPolice seize deadly weapons in
OL,4,Coperation to tackle violent crime
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police have seized
OL,7,Fa potentially deadly handgun in the
OL,8,FStockport area in an operation to
OL,9,Ftackle violent crime.
OL,11,FOperation Vulcan has been operating in
OL,12,FBrinnington for over three weeks.
OL,14,FOfficers searched a woodland area
OL,15,Falong Northumberland Road and
OL,16,Frecovered the weapon.
OL,18,FIt is to be assessed for its viability
OL,19,F- including if it has been illegally
OL,20,Fconverted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
