PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773129873
OL,3,CPolice seize deadly weapons in
OL,4,Coperation to tackle violent crime
OL,6,FThe recovery came just days into
OL,7,FVulcan's deployment to Brinnington,
OL,8,Fwhich aims to tackle drug-dealing,
OL,9,Fantisocial behaviour, and vehicle
OL,10,Fcrime and to take weapons off the
OL,11,Fstreets.
OL,13,FThe Vulcan team have seized four
OL,14,Ffirearms and more than fifty other
OL,15,Fweapons, including knives, machetes,
OL,16,Fand knuckle dusters.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
