FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773129873
OL,3,CPolice seize deadly weapons in
OL,4,Coperation to tackle violent crime
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Chris
OL,7,FJulien, from GMP's Operation Vulcan,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have been working in
OL,9,FBrinnington for just over three weeks,
OL,10,Fcarrying out a number of proactive
OL,11,Foperations during that time.
OL,13,F"Brinnington is a community full of
OL,14,Fgood, hard working people, and we are
OL,15,Fabsolutely committed to doing
OL,16,Feverything we can to protect them and
OL,17,Fsafeguard the area from criminality.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
