OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773129873
OL,3,CPolice seize deadly weapons in
OL,4,Coperation to tackle violent crime
OL,6,F"Seizing this firearm is an excellent
OL,7,Fresult for the team. While further
OL,8,Fassessments of the weapon are ongoing,
OL,9,Fremoving it from the streets prevents
OL,10,Fit from being used for any criminal
OL,11,Fpurpose.
OL,13,F"If you are in Brinnington and have
OL,14,Fany concerns, please do get in touch
OL,15,Fwith us. We will continue to maintain
OL,16,Fa visible presence in the area, and
OL,17,Fany intelligence you provide will be
OL,18,Fcarefully reviewed and acted upon."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@cO]
